    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Cahaya Aero Services Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, provides cargo and ground handling services in Indonesia. The company operates through two segments, Aviation and Non-Aviation. The Aviation segment includes various airport-related a encompasses services, including passenger and baggage handling, aircraft handling, provision and operation of ground support equipment, operation of business lounges and special services, cargo loading and unloading, cargo documentation, cargo transfer and transit handling, cargo storage and special cargo handling, and aircraft maintenance and repair services, as well as in-flight catering services. The Non-Aviation segment provides supporting services outside the scope of airport operational activities, including catering, housekeeping, laundry, gardening, accommodation, and transportation services. In addition, the company engages in trading, agency, representatives, services, transportation, and industrial activities. Further, the company is involved in the aircraft release and maintenance, facility management, catering, restaurant, and aviation training services. PT Cahaya Aero Services Tbk was founded in 1984 and is based in Tangerang, Indonesia.",
